Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.41,Renegade,,0,0,0,,Mati dan hidup berulang kali,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:36.67,Renegade,,0,0,0,,baru sampai di hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:44.15,Renegade,,0,0,0,,Usiaku sudah habis,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.47,Renegade,,0,0,0,,pada dasarnya tak diterima oleh Dao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.19,Renegade,,0,0,0,,Sedangkan dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:52.84,Renegade,,0,0,0,,tidak bersalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.91,Renegade,,0,0,0,,Selama sembilan belas tahun ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:10:00.19,Renegade,,0,0,0,,aku merasakan Xiao Ru'er tumbuh sedikit demi sedikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.79,Renegade,,0,0,0,,Jika harus mengambil tubuh anak ini untuk bangkit,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:06.15,Renegade,,0,0,0,,itu terlalu kejam baginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:08.50,Renegade,,0,0,0,,Senior,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.88,Renegade,,0,0,0,,Wan'er mengecewakanmu.
